<br>
Hopefully they'll give monks something that will compensate for this nerf.<br>
<br>
When the nerf went in place I got on my monk, was in KC, so I pulled a drolvarg sentry (dark blue con). Had some cleric buffs that put my HPs at 3043 or so.<br>
<br>
By the time the drolvarg was dead, I was down to 890 HPs, so it did roughly 2153 points of damage in the fight. Almost every hit he landed was for 80 - 100.<br>
<br>
The week before I was soloing these, unbuffed, not even SoW`d. My unbuffed HPs is 1999 HPs, and I could usually kill a drolvarg sentry and have about 45 - 65% health left. Meaning they used to do about 900 - 1300 HPs in damage.<br>
<br>
