     I logged on the other day and with fairly good gear (fungi, sshs, Amy Staff) got my ass handed to me in KC by sentry's (the same ones I solo'd a day before). Went outside to DL and found that things were just as bad even with the light blues. I looked to my guild for support (I can't imagine being anything but supportive to others if this happened to them) only to find none. People were openly bashing me in the guild channel, I just wanted to be sick.<br>
     I don't know much about visions and where things are going, but I do know that I'm upset that I've paid into something for over 3 years to have this happen. Its hard to actually cancel my accout, but if nothing changes in the next week then its Verant's way of telling us politely (or rudely) its time to leave (don't let the door hit you in the butt). I'm not sure what they want, but I guess its not my money anymore. I too will never buy another product from this company and strongly encourage others to do the same.<br>
<br>
Gujoryu<br>
Lvl 54 Monk (Legacy of Twilight)<br>
